<subSubSection pageId="12" pageNumber="141" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="12.[1358,2566,718,1458]" pageId="12" pageNumber="141">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1360,1706,1226,1259]" pageId="12" pageNumber="141">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. The Rufous Mouse Opossum has a widespread distribution and presumably a large global population, with a lack of major conservation threats.
</paragraph>
